media:group.media:title: The PragerU Halloween Special 2022
media:group.media:description: It was a cold, dark, and stormy Halloween night. As the rain poured from the dark clouds above, thunder cracked through the night sky. A group of leftist trick-or-treaters dressed up as a ghoul, Che Guevara, Karl Marx, and an evil health director look for a place to keep dry. What they found would change their lives forever.
